description: If you’re jonesing for a refreshingly healthy beverage or snack, just know that Nicole Juicery is making its way through all of LA, fueling bodies and souls with their exotic smoothies, fresh juices, and health-boost bowls. Their whole selection is exclusively gluten-free, vegan, and organic, so you’re sure to be back at Nicole Juicery again & again for all your deliciously fruity and nutritional needs.
name: Nicole Juicery
